item.title: All Class8 ints
item.dc:creator: @Jordiescape Jordiescape
item.description:
@Jordiescape wrote:

Isn’t that easy enough to figure out yourself? Ones i’ve found in about one second of looking in class8:

anInt165 - male model ID anInt200 - female model ID anIntArray156 - amount of old colours anIntArray160 - amount of new colours anInt181 - zoom anInt174 - inv and ground model
I’m sure you can find some more yourself.
